                            <comment id="14035554" author="epahomov" created="Wed, 18 Jun 2014 10:24:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yep, I used patched version of spark. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14085834" author="apachespark" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 05:41:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;andrewor14&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/1777&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/1777&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14085835" author="andrewor" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 05:42:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=aash&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;aash&quot;&gt;aash&lt;/a&gt; I have built my changes on top of yours in my PR. It would be good if you could take a look.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14085932" author="aash" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 07:34:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks great!  I made one comment, but this definitely captures the spirit of my changes and I&apos;m very happy to see this effort getting attention.  Many thanks Andrew!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
